#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Drives that are automounted at login cannot be used as paths. Such drives "
"will be reverted to defaults during restart of &plasma;."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Desktop path:"
msgstr "Putanja površi:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Desktop folder contains all the files which you see in a "
"<guilabel>Folder View</guilabel> widget on your desktop. The default path is "
"usually <filename class=\"directory\">~/Desktop</filename> but you can "
"change here the location of this folder."
msgstr ""
"Fascikla površi sadrži sve fajlove koje vidite u vidžetu prikaza fascikle na "
"površi. Podrazumevana putanja je obično <filename class=\"directory\">~/"
"Desktop</filename>, ali možete i promeniti lokaciju ove fascikle."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Documents path:"
msgstr "Putanja dokumenata:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This folder will be used by default to load or save documents from or to."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je fascikla iz koje se dokumenti podrazumevano učitavaju i upisuju."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:74
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Download path:"
msgid "Downloads path:"
msgstr "Putanja preuzimanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "This folder will be used by default to save your downloaded items."
msgstr "Ovo je fascikla u koju se podrazumevano upisuju preuzete stavke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:78
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Movies path:"
msgid "Videos path:"
msgstr "Putanja filmova:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "This folder will be used by default to load or save movies from or to."
msgstr "Ovo je fascikla iz koje se filmovi podrazumevano učitavaju i upisuju."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pictures path:"
msgstr "Putanja slika:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This folder will be used by default to load or save pictures from or to."
msgstr "Ovo je fascikla iz koje se slike podrazumevano učitavaju i upisuju."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Music path:"
msgstr "Putanja muzike:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "This folder will be used by default to load or save music from or to."
msgstr "Ovo je fascikla iz koje se muzika podrazumevana učitava i upisuje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you change a path and click <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> a dialog appears "
"where you can choose to move the content to the new folder or use the new "
"folder without moving the files."
msgstr ""
"Ako promenite putanju i kliknete na <guibutton>Primeni</guibutton>, iskače "
"dijalog u kojem možete izabrati da premestite sadržaj u novu fasciklu, ili "
"da pređete na novu fasciklu bez premeštanja fajlova."

